episodes.title: This Cult Spent $500,000 to Make a Minecraft Mod
episodes.description:
Not many know the outright bizarre backstory of Nightmare Craft, the world's most expensive Minecraft mod made by members of Twin Flames Universe. Today we're gonna go over a story of narcissism, spiritual lunacy, the internet, and the world's most popular video game.

Thumbnail made by https://www.instagram.com/kar.atart/

All music is by me and can be found under the artist name "NeverEndingCorridor" on all major streaming platforms

While I tried to use publicly available TFU footage wherever possible, many of the ascension school class and in-person workshop clips comes from the Netflix and Prime documentaries.
